details.text:
This section contains a summary of the area and fmax data generated by compiling the kernels through Quartus. 
To generate the data, run a Quartus compile on the project created for this design. 
To run the Quartus compile, please run command without flag -c, -rtl or -march=emulator

children.name: Run Quartus compile to populate this section. See details for more information.
